<L>__{interior warehouse day}
<A>__{the stretcher with jacob blasts through a wall and starts to race across the floor of the building that jacob had been sweeping up the day before. it careens along, actually taking a few turns, like it has a mind of its own, heading for a shallow pit in the middle of the warehouse. the stretcher hits the pit, drops a bit, swings up violently, and stops in a vertical position like a rake that has been stepped on and a black human shape shoots out of jacob's body from intertial force, staying upright as it slides across the floor, spins, stops, then changes into:}
<B>__{freddy krueger}
