<D>__{aw, poor baby's homesick, isn't he? don't worry. we'll all be one happy family soon. wanna be the first recruit?}
<A>__{freddy raises his blades and swings. the straps around jacob drop away as his body falls to the floor. he scrambles to his feet and starts to run. freddy laughs with jacob running as he heads for a door. before he gets there, the door swings open and freddy leans casually in his way.}
<C>__{freddy }
<D>__{what's the matter? don't want to be part of my expansion project?}
<A>__{jacob turns right around and races back across the warehouse.}
<B>__{at the dumpster}
