<D>__{it's our job.}
<C>__{freddy}
<D>__{get a new one.}
<A>__{and freddy starts to spin. slowly at first, then faster and faster, until his image starts to blur. the police circle the whirling image, holding back to see what will happen nexterior krueger stops spinning. and his clothes are different. his red and green stripes have been replaced by black and white ones. there is a number printed across his chest. he's dressed like a convict. freddy grins.}
<C>__{freddy }
<D>__{time to blow this jointerior}
